Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.stevensheaves.data.model.Customer
  • public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used for storing all data related to a Customer There are multiple constructors in the class to account for the multiple use cases where not all data may be available or required.
